I'm the founder of Those Awesome Guys, a small indie studio

10
00:00:26,601 --> 00:00:28,262
formed out of people from all over the world.

11
00:00:29,063 --> 00:00:32,045
We made a game called Move or Die for a player friendship

12
00:00:32,085 --> 00:00:34,146
ruining game that came out last year.

13
00:00:34,166 --> 00:00:36,108
And I go to a lot of events.

14
00:00:36,428 --> 00:00:38,649
And I love talking about games because they're awesome.

15
00:00:39,410 --> 00:00:41,611
And in order to illustrate this, I

16
00:00:41,671 --> 00:00:44,393
figured I should take a photo of all of my badges.

17
00:00:45,374 --> 00:00:47,696
And I took this photo when I started working on these slides.

18
00:00:47,896 --> 00:00:50,738
And by the time I was done, I had to take an extra photo.

