00:22:50,262 --> 00:22:52,143
very hard to talk about showcasing your game,

541
00:22:53,563 --> 00:22:54,784
because it's hard doing it.

542
00:22:55,024 --> 00:22:58,645
So you probably try to learn more about this

543
00:22:58,705 --> 00:23:00,525
by reading what other developers did.

544
00:23:01,005 --> 00:23:02,746
And writing a postmortem is your way

545
00:23:02,906 --> 00:23:04,286
of giving back to the community.

546
00:23:04,446 --> 00:23:05,467
So please do this.

547
00:23:07,327 --> 00:23:08,668
Don't forget about contest winners,

548
00:23:08,908 --> 00:23:12,631
in case you had contests with winners

549
00:23:13,131 --> 00:23:15,953
announced after the event, because we forgot about that

