00:24:07,339 --> 00:24:10,902
I had to zoom in to see PAX there,

573
00:24:11,322 --> 00:24:13,724
and it was lower than the previous day.

574
00:24:14,444 --> 00:24:15,765
So yeah, here are some more.

575
00:24:15,785 --> 00:24:17,306
You can take photos of these.

576
00:24:17,487 --> 00:24:18,888
You can find them in the vault.

577
00:24:19,648 --> 00:24:23,251
Events don't bring you sales, so please keep this in mind.

578
00:24:24,092 --> 00:24:25,412
But they bring you something better.

579
00:24:26,792 --> 00:24:28,012
And here are some examples.

